"runtimeMs":113352,"childSessions":["agent:master-orchestrator:subagent:8d8e1952-016d-4c2d-819c-c3b32e3b45b2","agent:master-orchestrator:subagent:cd3256cb-3b94-49db-84de-ab99c44cf2fd","agent:master-orchestrator:subagent:aa7da6a2-9c14-4261-b1b7-936fb3c60ec8","agent:master-orchestrator:subagent:53ffecba-7a14-43e4-91be-9b3efcc56072","agent:master-orchestrator:subagent:5d2b77de-dd66-41c2-b053-30aabd324a0e","agent:master-orchestrator:subagent:8bffa95f-1686-4571-a0ed-e69d265eb964"],"systemSent":true,"abortedLastRun":false,"lastChannel":"telegram","lastTo":"telegram:6053576134","lastAccountId":"main_bot","transcriptPath":"/root/.openclaw/agents/master-orchestrator/sessions/8e18daec-1780-455f-b7c4-896849ef86be.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The workspace has no git! That means the bug fixes we made to the DTLX backend code are NOT in any git repo. The fixes are only in the local dist/ folder. This is a problem.\n\nNow let me report back to Lead about the GitLab CI situation:\n\n1. **Pipeline is not slow** — there are NO running pipelines at all\n2. **Last pipeline**: 2026-03-30 (15 days ago), MR !166 — passed successfully  \n3. **Pipeline speed**: ~3 minutes (not slow when it runs)\n4. **Current MR !166**: mergeable, no new pipelines needed\n\n\n5. **The real issue**: Our local bug fixes aren't committed to the feature branch since there's no git repo here, so the CI pipeline reflects the codebase from two weeks ago. The shared runners might be unavailable or have changed their status."},{"type":"text","text":"---\n\n## 🌐 GitLab CI Check — DTLX Backend\n\n### Tình trạng pipeline\n\n| Item | Status |\n|---|---|\n| Pipeline running | **NONE** (không có pipeline nào đang chạy) |\n| Pipeline cuối | **2026-03-30** (15 ngày trước) — MR !166 ✅ success |\n| Thời gian chạy | **~3 phút** — không chậm |\n| MR !166 | **Mergeable** — có thể merge ngay |\n\n### Không phải attack — vấn đề thực sự:\n\n**GitLab không nhận được code mới từ 15 ngày qua.**\n\nCommits mới nhất trên `feature/clean-architecture-migration`:\n```\n47d53ae1 — 2026-03-30 09:14 (15 ngày trước) — \"chore: course student repository\"\n4a570ad6 — 2026-03-30 09:12 — \"chore: remove folder openspec\"\n27f375b8 — 2026-03-30 09:08 — \"chore: implement prettier\"\n```\n\n**Các bug fix hôm nay chưa được push lên git** — workspace DTLX BE hiện tại **không có git**. Code chạy local trong `dist/` nhưng không có repo git để push lên GitLab.\n\n### Hướng xử lý\n\nMuốn đẩy các bug fix (4 bugs đã fix) lên GitLab để trigger pipeline không?"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":123,"output":549,"totalTokens":147883,"cacheRead":145105,"cacheWrite":2106,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776162143517,"responseId":"062d486107384787d72be69212a976dc","__openclaw":{"id":"02d899f5","seq":1257}}]},{"key":"agent:master-orchestrator:cron:e7885813-0446-4101-a171-941c2416848e","kind":"other","channel":"unknown","label":"Cron: Agent Status to Lead","displayName":"Cron: Agent Status to Lead","updatedAt":1776161007428,"sessionId":"40a942b3-5a9f-4ed5-9987-0043388e1ea2","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","contextTokens":200000,"totalTokens":33213,"estimatedCostUsd":0,"status":"running","startedAt":1776161006770,"systemSent":true,"abortedLastRun":false,"transcriptPath":"/root/.openclaw/agents/master-orchestrator/sessions/40a942b3-5a9f-4ed5-9987-0043388e1ea2.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"assistant","content":[],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"totalTokens":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"aborted","timestamp":1776161080428,"errorMessage":"Request was aborted.","__openclaw":{"id":"d2dd28b1","seq":6}}]},{"key":"agent:master-orchestrator:cron:ac986a8d-2425-40c7-835b-ed9b101b0bff","kind":"other","channel":"unknown","label":"Cron: Send this exact message to Telegram group -5163901258:","displayName":"