concise for the group.\n\nThe main changes since the last report are the QLHV group coming online and DTLX going offline—both sessions cycling naturally. There are no new failures or blockers beyond what we already know, so I'll send this as a concise update.","thinkingSignature":"7094319c7df859fd7db73e3e53361c27148dd52edb057928a97421b55e9cc4a7"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_9ykfjky1v071_1","name":"memory_search","arguments":{"query":"heartbeat state active sessions last report","maxResults":3}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":29065,"output":523,"cacheRead":13944,"cacheWrite":417,"totalTokens":43949,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776163651114,"responseId":"062d4e4452e9eaa599ecfe0abdb8b1dd"}}
{"type":"message","id":"7d0a80d9","parentId":"e221b7fe","timestamp":"2026-04-14T10:47:47.716Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_9ykfjky1v071_1","toolName":"memory_search","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"results\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"07cdf349780f84851f44e5ab68761cdbe5f6e4a62559b8fbf3f07e739935bf41\",\n      \"path\": \"memory/dtlx-context.md\",\n      \"startLine\": 1,\n      \"endLine\": 46,\n      \"score\": 0.7405801153101165,\n      \"textScore\": 0.7405801153101165,\n      \"snippet\": \"# AHV DTLX Project Context\\n\\n_Last updated: 2026-04-12 by Orbis_\\n\\n## ⚠️ CRITICAL — System Architecture\\n\\n**DTLX và QLHV là 2 hệ thống DÙNG CHUNG database:**\\n\\n```\\nDTLX (MASTER) ─────────────────── QLHV (SUBSYSTEM)\\n   Hệ thống chính                    Tách ra cho THẦY/GV\\n   Ban giám đốc, Sales, Admin        Giáo viên quản lý HV\\n        │                                 │\\n        └──────── SHARED MONGODB ────────┘\\n              103.253.21.98:27017\\n```\\n\\n**→ QLHV phải đồng bộ dữ liệu với DTLX luôn luôn.**\\n**→ Khi dev QLHV, phải HIỂU DTLX schema vì cùng DB.**\\n\\n## Project Identity\\n- **DTLX Name**: AHV DTLX (Đào Tạo Lái Xe) — MASTER\\n- **QLHV Name**: AHV QLHV (Quản Lý Học Viên) — SUBSYSTEM\\n- **Telegram\\n\\nSource: memory/dtlx-context.md#L1-L46\",\n      \"source\": \"memory\",\n      \"citation\": \"memory/dtlx-context.md#L1-L46\",\n      \"corpus\": \"memory\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"89ccf26b7040ce021e9526b7117935aab4b4418e9afc2e7f38a71f602ec196dd\",\n      \"path\": \"memory/2026-04-14.md\",\n      \"startLine\": 21,\n      \"endLine\": 41,\n      \"score\": 0.7222095086420897,\n      \"textScore\": 0.7222095086420897,\n      \"snippet\": \"3. `/users/sales/counter` → 500: `docCounter[0] || {}` for empty aggregate\\n  4. `/lessons/detail-by-date` → server crash: route reorder (`/:id` catchall moved after specific routes)\\n  5. `/teacher-infos` → 404: added `router.get('/')` route\\n\\n## 08: