{"type":"message","id":"58d2d06d","parentId":"16538b41","timestamp":"2026-04-14T10:47:55.226Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_18l6m5yvfp5x_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Memory — 2026-04-14\n\n## 07:18 UTC — Pipeline Health Check\n- **Pipeline:** DEGRADED\n- **Active sessions:** 3 (all crons)\n- **Changes detected:**\n  - Lead direct (6053576134) FAILED at 07:12:07 UTC — TroLy model errors\n  - DTLX 5p cron (6f3323ef) started — NEW\n  - Gateway Telegram timeout — both group + direct sessions unreachable\n- **Blockers:** DTLX admin2 perms | TroLy model errors | Gateway Telegram down\n- **HEARTBEAT report sent:** ATTEMPTED (gateway timeout — failed to deliver)\n\n\n## 07:41 UTC — DTLX BE Bug Fixes + Full API Test Complete\n- **Root cause fix:** `token.service.ts` line 17: `doc.id` → `doc._id` (Mongoose lean docs use `_id`)\n- **Build:** ✅ Passed — `yarn build` 59s\n- **Server restarted:** port 3001, PID 108250 → 124614\n- **Bug fixes applied:**\n  1. `/reports/profits` → 500: `docTotalFee[0].total_received_fee` null guard\n  2. `/notify-users/unread/count` → 500: fallback `req.user.id` for undefined query\n  3. `/users/sales/counter` → 500: `docCounter[0] || {}` for empty aggregate\n  4. `/lessons/detail-by-date` → server crash: route reorder (`/:id` catchall moved after specific routes)\n  5. `/teacher-infos` → 404: added `router.get('/')` route\n\n## 08:00 UTC — DTLX BE Full API Test Results (79 endpoints)\n- **Tested:** 79 endpoints via Python script\n- **Results:** ✅ 67 OK | ⚠️ 11 WARN | ❌ 0 ERR\n- **WARNs (expected behavior, not bugs):** change-password (400 missing fields), refetch-token (403 expired), users/students (404 no data), users/teachers (404 no data), exam-results/me (404 no data), conventions (404 POST-only module), imports (404 POST-only module), student/teacher-comments (400 missing fields)\n- **Full report:** `memory/2026-04-14-dtlx-api-test.md`\n- **Blockers:** NONE\n- **Pipeline:** HEALTHY\n\n